* Copy the 'client' folder somewhere in your Web server

* Copy 'config.php.dist' to 'config.php' and edit accordingly

* Download simplepie (http://simplepie.org/) and install it in a folder
	named 'simplepie' in the 'client' one

* Create a file name 'feed' and give it read access from your webserver 

* Go to 'register.php' and register a query at a particular sparqlPuSH service

* Once registered, updates will be pushed to your endpoint and can be observed at 'index.php'